arStrings.szText: Years ago, I ran a mercenary company out of this place. The Pale Hand. I had less to lose, then.
But now the fight’s been brought to me—and I think I’d be more use to you as a mercenary, a “shield for hire”, if you will, than a smith. Though there’s a chance you’ll get both out of me.

And my name still carries weight. The other mercenaries will be more likely to return if I am here. And you will need their help, my friend. You will never regret hiring one of the Pale Hand into your service.
